LineAccounts is a Form
    restrict action Create
    restrict action InterfaceCreate
    restrict action Delete
    Actions
        action is Delete
            hide when invalid
        action is save
            hide when invalid
    Layout
        display as text
            paragraph
                BillingInvoice.InvoicePrefix
                    label is "Invoice"
                BillingInvoice.ConditionalInvoiceNumber
                    no label
                BillingInvoiceLine
                    label is "Line"
            SalesAccount
                label is "SalesAccount"
                compact format
            OffsetAccount
                label is "OffsetAccount"
                compact format
            COGSAccount
                label is "COGSAccount"
                compact format
